{"id":8004,"date":"2021-10-24T09:39:21","date_gmt":"2021-10-24T02:39:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=8004"},"modified":"2023-11-22T12:51:06","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T05:51:06","slug":"cang-cai-mep-thi-vai-duoc-danh-gia-cao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/cang-cai-mep-thi-vai-duoc-danh-gia-cao-so-voi-khu-vuc\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p &#8211; Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n v\u1ec1 v\u1eadn t\u1ea3i bi\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam, m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5c v\u1eadn t\u1ea3i t\u1eeb <strong>c\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9, \u00c2u c\u00f2n l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat c\u00e1c h\u00e0ng trung chuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e0ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf C\u00e1i M\u00e9p &#8211; Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i tham gia v\u00e0o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u1edbn c\u00e1c c\u1ea3ng trung chuy\u1ec3n trong khu v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8013\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8013\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8013 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dsc2204-jpg-9961-1592478466.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/531;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8013\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8013\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dsc2204-jpg-9961-1592478466.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i\" width=\"800\" height=\"531\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8013\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p \u2013 Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean gia B\u0110S c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ch\u1ec9n chu, \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <strong>Vinhome Land<\/strong> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00e0y nh\u00e9<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/vinhomes-grand-park\/\"><strong>C\u0103n h\u1ed9 Vinhomes Grand Park Qu\u1eadn 9<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0i n\u00e9t th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3ng Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i &#8211; C\u00e1i M\u00e9p l\u00e0 c\u1ee5m c\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i B\u00e0 R\u1ecba &#8211; V\u0169ng T\u00e0u, ngay t\u1ea1i c\u1eeda S.Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i v\u00e0 S.C\u00e1i M\u00e9p. C\u1ea3ng Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf C\u00e1i M\u00e9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c t\u00e0u container c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea3i\u00a0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 80.000 DWT v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t th\u00f4ng qua l\u00e0 600-700 ngh\u00ecn TEU trong m\u1ed7i n\u0103m. C\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t c\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 1,6-2 tri\u1ec7u t\u1ea5n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m.\u00a0<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8019\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8019\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8019 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/400;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8019\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8019\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8019\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo C\u1ee5c H\u00e0ng h\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n trong khu v\u1ef1c C\u00e1i M\u00e9p &#8211; Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfm \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 50% t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qua c\u00e1c c\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p \u2013 Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba l\u00fd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1\u00a0<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea3ng l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh trong khu v\u1ef1c<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c n\u1ea1o v\u00e9t lu\u1ed3ng s\u00f4ng v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i giao th\u00f4ng cho c\u1ee5m c\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh ngang h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi Singapore.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quan \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u1edf t\u1ea1i c\u1ea3ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf C\u00e1i M\u00e9p &#8211; Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20\/3.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110NB ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n l\u00e0 nh\u1edd c\u00f3 c\u1ea3ng. Ri\u00eang n\u0103m 2020, c\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 g\u1ea7n 113 tri\u1ec7u t\u1ea5n h\u00e0ng ho\u00e1 ra v\u00e0o, chi\u1ebfm 16% t\u1ed5ng h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm 34% t\u1ed5ng h\u00e0ng container th\u00f4ng qua c\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8020\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8020\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8020 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/ttxvn-cang-cai-mep-1.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ph\u00fac \u0111ang ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20\/3\" width=\"800\" height=\"569\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/569;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8020\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8020\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/ttxvn-cang-cai-mep-1.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ph\u00fac \u0111ang ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20\/3\" width=\"800\" height=\"569\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8020\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng Nguy\u1ec5n Xu\u00e2n Ph\u00fac \u0111ang ki\u1ec3m tra t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 20\/3<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ng\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3ng bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 chu\u1ed7i cung \u1ee9ng logistic.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1o c\u00e1o v\u1edbi Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng th\u00ec \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Th\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh n\u1eb1m trong v\u00f9ng kinh t\u1ebf tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf ph\u00eda Nam v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y Nam B\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 51 l\u00e0 duy nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y \u0111ang qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i, lu\u00f4n ch\u1ecbu \u00e1ch t\u1eafc giao th\u00f4ng, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi c\u1ee5m c\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p &#8211; Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Th\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f3 t\u00ednh k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho vi\u1ec7c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a nh\u01b0 tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eaft Bi\u00ean H\u00f2a &#8211; V\u0169ng T\u00e0u, hay \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 4 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c n\u00fat kh\u00e1c \u1edf tr\u00ean qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 51&#8230; v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 &#8220;h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea5p b\u00e1ch&#8221;.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8017 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/lo5.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p - Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8017\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/lo5.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p - Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c n\u1ea1o v\u00e9t lu\u1ed3ng s\u00f4ng, t\u0103ng th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2u xu\u1ed1ng \u00e2m 15,5 m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c t\u00e0u l\u1edbn h\u01a1n;ngo\u00e0i ra v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i giao th\u00f4ng, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi cao t\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ed \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u1ea1o v\u00e9t lu\u1ed3ng s\u00f4ng cho c\u00e1c t\u00e0u l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o cao t\u1ed1c Bi\u00ean H\u00f2a &#8211; V\u0169ng T\u00e0u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u Ph\u01b0\u1edbc An.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/grand-marina-sai-gon-ba-son-quan-1\/\"><strong>C\u0103n h\u1ed9 Grand Marina Saigon Qu\u1eadn 1<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i c\u1ee5m c\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i\u00a0<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do c\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i TP.H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c c\u1ee1 t\u00e0u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1edf l\u1edbn h\u01a1n 3 ngh\u00ecn TEU, v\u00ec v\u1eady n\u00ean h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c container xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u trong khu v\u1ef1c v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i trung chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3ng trung chuy\u1ec3n c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u01a1\u0301c trong khu v\u01b0\u0323c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho m\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t TEU container khi \u0111em \u0111i xu\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9u s\u1ebd t\u1ed1n th\u00eam g\u1ea7n 200 USD cho chi ph\u00ed b\u1ed1c x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng, chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ea3i l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ebfn c\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8011 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/cang-thi-vai-cai-mep-5.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p - Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"453\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/453;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8011\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/cang-thi-vai-cai-mep-5.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p - Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"453\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu trung t\u00e2m trung chuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh, h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a xu\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng xa, th\u00ec \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 29% kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e1c container xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u nh\u00f3m c\u1ea3ng s\u1ed1 5 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n trung chuy\u1ec3n qua c\u00e1c c\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i Singapore hay Hongkong.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng v\u1eadn t\u1ea3i bi\u1ec3n \u0111i xa c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam, m\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ebfn v\u1eadn t\u1ea3i t\u1eeb C\u00e1i M\u00e9p \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 M\u1ef9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat c\u00e1c h\u00e0ng trung chuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e0ngC\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1edbn c\u00e1c c\u1ea3ng trung chuy\u1ec3n trong khu v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i \u00edch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a kinh t\u1ebf trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0110NB m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u1edf t\u1ea7m qu\u1ed1c gia.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p &#8211; Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ebfn t\u00e0u kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u 22 th\u00e1ng 3, t\u00e0u MSC Auriga c\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3ng SSIT t\u1ea1i c\u1ee5m c\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p &#8211; Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i. T\u00e0u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ebfp d\u1ee1 &gt; 15.000 Teus &#8211; k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e0u n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8018 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/photo-0-1507532187606.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p - Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/530;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8018\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/photo-0-1507532187606.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p - Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0u n\u00e0y d\u00e0i t\u1edbi 366 m\u00e9t v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea3i x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 160 ngh\u00ecn t\u1ea5n v\u00e0 ch\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi 15 ngh\u00ecn Teus trong \u0111\u00f3 1 Teu t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi 1 container 20 feet.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi k\u1ebft! Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng <strong>C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn khu v\u1ef1c l\u00e2n c\u1eadn. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed xung quanh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch xung quanh, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 hay kh\u00f4ng. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 B\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ed9ng S\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/\">vinhomeland.com.vn<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;8004&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (1 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;C\u1ea3ng C\u00e1i M\u00e9p - Th\u1ecb V\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;118&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kk